{"tid":1334714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發 有圖] 3M出咗香港版廣告","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:54:54.000Z","uid":28870,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"078f6e39cb7b25362bdc17d4996f0a4bc683a49e","tid":1334714,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">SORRY FOR CLICKBAIT</span></span><br />\n民陣上訴被推翻 警方擺出強硬姿態<br />\n相信但大家都好清楚 聽日會發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n買罩=買旅遊保險咁<br />\n唔係話買咗你就要去自爆<br />\n純粹係買個保障<br />\n無論你係衝擊、想撤退、想做FA、想運物資<br />\n有面罩 起碼確保你可以周圍行先 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔會因為環境有變 而不能進場/離場</span></span></strong><br />\n見過好多手足因為食咗tg 搞到眼都睜唔開 行都行唔到<br />\n<br />\n其實買個罩真係冇大家想像中咁貴<br />\n基本款 勉強擋到<br />\n3M 3320面罩+3311濾棉 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">(大概100蚊</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6acj2LL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6acj2LL.jpg&h=12eabdf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階款 一定擋到<br />\n6200面罩+P100濾罐 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">(大概250蚊</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPc4uqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPc4uqx.jpg&h=029478ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n我係度呼籲大家<br />\n無論如何 一定要買定個罩</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n買物資黎嘅手足 都咪再買醫療口罩啊  <br />\n就算係N95都冇用架"},{"pid":"973e95c654acd07d671628d25c46ab42da551760","tid":1334714,"uid":30163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 全部人同我出去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.g